”—ظRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2024-05-18-twin0247.mdظ@9297903261c5391a7a585e56cc625b48123af0ebbf13cd2d79270d2d2fb95722¹This week in Nushell #247‘§NushellعIanManske made a huge internal change, replacing 
``ExternalStream``
 with a new 
``ByteStream``
 type (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12774] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12887] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12886] 3
). Also lots of other improvements: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12871] removed usages of 
``Call::positional_nth``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12867] fixed a 
``char``
 panic
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12861] removed stack debug assert
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12848] preserved metadata in more places
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12846] fixed a 
``sys``
 panic
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12838] updated the PR template
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12833] fixed custom converters with 
``save``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12511] added 
``Span``
 merging functions
.
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12896] excluded polars from ensure_plugins_built() for performance reasons
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12895] fixed the way the output of 
``table``
 is printed in 
``print()``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12788] modified 
``collect``
 to not require a closure
.
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12888] allowed defining 
``it``
 as a variable inside closures
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12879] enabled passing float values to custom commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12868] improved messages for incomplete string errors
.
francesco-gaglione 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12826] merged tests to produce a single binary
.
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12881] synced up with reedline changes
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12875] made it clearer what is being loaded with --log-level info
.
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12878] fixed syntax shape requirements for --quantiles option for polars summary
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12819] allowed custom value operations to work on eager and lazy dataframes interchangeably
.
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12877] fixed a small error in the help examples for the get command
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12876] improved help for 
``each while``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12864] added search terms for the 
``compact``
 command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12844] added an example and search term for 'repeat' to the 
``fill``
 command
.
cablehead 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12865] added a passing test for interactivity on slow pipelines
.
ExaltedBagel 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12860] fixed a panic when exploring an empty dictionary
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12820] fixed improperly escaped strings in 
``stor insert``
.
cptpiepmatz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12857] added 
``Stack::stdout_file``
 and 
``Stack::stderr_file``
 to capture stdout/-err of external commands
.
’گگع>Title: This week in Nushell #247
Path: Nushell
Content:
IanManske made a huge internal change, replacing 
``ExternalStream``
 with a new 
``ByteStream``
 type (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12774] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12887] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12886] 3
). Also lots of other improvements: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12871] removed usages of 
``Call::positional_nth``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12867] fixed a 
``char``
 panic
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12861] removed stack debug assert
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12848] preserved metadata in more places
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12846] fixed a 
``sys``
 panic
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12838] updated the PR template
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12833] fixed custom converters with 
``save``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12511] added 
``Span``
 merging functions
.
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12896] excluded polars from ensure_plugins_built() for performance reasons
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12895] fixed the way the output of 
``table``
 is printed in 
``print()``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12788] modified 
``collect``
 to not require a closure
.
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12888] allowed defining 
``it``
 as a variable inside closures
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12879] enabled passing float values to custom commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12868] improved messages for incomplete string errors
.
francesco-gaglione 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12826] merged tests to produce a single binary
.
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12881] synced up with reedline changes
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12875] made it clearer what is being loaded with --log-level info
.
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12878] fixed syntax shape requirements for --quantiles option for polars summary
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12819] allowed custom value operations to work on eager and lazy dataframes interchangeably
.
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12877] fixed a small error in the help examples for the get command
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12876] improved help for 
``each while``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12864] added search terms for the 
``compact``
 command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12844] added an example and search term for 'repeat' to the 
``fill``
 command
.
cablehead 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12865] added a passing test for interactivity on slow pipelines
.
ExaltedBagel 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12860] fixed a panic when exploring an empty dictionary
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12820] fixed improperly escaped strings in 
``stor insert``
.
cptpiepmatz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12857] added 
``Stack::stdout_file``
 and 
``Stack::stderr_file``
 to capture stdout/-err of external commands
.
